WEBVTT

00:10.511 --> 00:12.343
Here you go.

00:15.749 --> 00:16.982
Take care, honey.

00:17.017 --> 00:18.816
Bye, aunt gina.

00:18.852 --> 00:21.653
Tell your mom
I'll call her tomorrow.

00:21.688 --> 00:24.022
A bientot.
Au revoir, mademoiselle!

